{
  "stem": "142.6",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Outcry always, but rebellion, I didn't see it.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Where would we go?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "No, the Germans were-- they let anybody know, if [INAUDIBLE] they will kill you, probably, right away.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So nothing happens that I didn't see that.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "More than the necessary--",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah, always.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They-- they tried to push as much as they could, the Germans.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They want to-- to finish with-- with the people.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, they were pretty good at how much they can put extra, you know.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Always they would find a place to push them in.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I didn't see anything that-- they didn't have any other way, you know.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Where were they going to live?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Out?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "For what?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "They couldn't put it back in another.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Everything was very specific with their numbers, you know.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, yeah, yeah.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They-- they knew how many.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And they knew how many extra could put them in.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The only thing you hear is-- is the scratching on the walls.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "That's what I hear myself.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They're scratching the walls.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They know-- they-- they know all the way.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I-- I think-- I don't know.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I don't know if it was a German, or the capos did most of the work.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You know.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They closed the door.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I mean, it's not too much.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And when you are there, you know, everybody's-- they don't wait too long, you know.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well they were always ready upstairs to, you know, their signals, you know, you put them in.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It doesn't take too long, you know.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I mean the-- the Zyklon B, whatever, Zyklon B, when the gas gets with the air or something-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] you're finished.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, I-- I don't.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "There was a procedure-- very, very, simple, I think.",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
